[SN]TITLE[SN]
Adele wins four Brit Awards

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Adele was the big winner at last night's Brit Awards. She scooped four gongs.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
25 February 2016 Last updated at 07:08 GMT
She took home British female solo artist, British single, British global success award and British album of the year.
She was even presented with one of her awards from Tim Peake on the International Space Station.
Coldplay won Best British Group while Justin Bieber won Best International Male.
Lots of big names were at the awards including Ellie Goulding, Little Mix, Fleur and Nick Grimshaw.
Martin was on the red carpet for Newsround.
